title: Lauren Boebert
deleted: Boebert supports the end of the children's program [[Sesame Street]], noting that the characters involved promote a left-wing radical agenda. This falls in line with other state politicians from Colorado.<ref name="heraldtimes"/>

title: Lauren Boebert
added: According to the ''[[Grand Junction Daily Sentinel]]'', "Court records also show that from 2011 to last year (2019), Boebert had been cited for numerous traffic offenses in Garfield, Clear Creek and Larimer counties, including speeding, following too closely to another vehicle, driving with expired license plates and several citations for failure to use a seatbelt and failure to use proper child restraints."<ref>Ashby, Charles (September 21, 2020) [https://www.gjsentinel.com/news/western_colorado/boeberts-democratic-upbringing-questioned/article_599f9890-f867-11ea-a66d-836e16473c98.html "Boebert's Democratic upbringing questioned."] Daily Sentinel. (Retrieved October 8, 2010.)</ref>
